Class TrafficLightGroup

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.objects.trafficlight.TrafficLightGroup
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, ToDataOutput
public class TrafficLightGroup extends Object implements Serializable, ToDataOutput
Class represents a group of traffic lights that together control a junction.
